Hey, Charley!

1537
02:11:12,824 --> 02:11:15,909
Looks like the doc
changed his mind about you.

1538
02:11:22,583 --> 02:11:24,751
Something wrong?

1539
02:11:24,835 --> 02:11:26,503
No.
Everything's fine.

1540
02:11:26,587 --> 02:11:28,797
I forgot to tell you
I'll have word about the saloon

1541
02:11:28,881 --> 02:11:29,840
by the time you get back.

1542
02:11:29,923 --> 02:11:31,716
Sounds good.

1543
02:11:33,427 --> 02:11:35,012
You take care, now.

1544
02:11:36,597 --> 02:11:39,098
Charley.

1545
02:11:39,183 --> 02:11:40,224
Sue.

1546
02:11:40,308 --> 02:11:41,976
I'll be along.

1547
02:11:47,064 --> 02:11:48,899
Saloon?

1548
