1552
02:12:04,331 --> 02:12:06,332
Not even half.

1553
02:12:06,373 --> 02:12:09,959
Well let the brains of the outfith
do the thinking.

1554
02:12:10,002 --> 02:12:18,384
Sue!

1555
02:12:18,427 --> 02:12:22,263
You are coming back, aren't you?

1556
02:12:22,305 --> 02:12:27,684
And I will be waiting for you Charles!

1557
02:12:31,396 --> 02:12:36,735
Keep nothing private.

1558
02:12:36,819 --> 02:12:42,073
Have to go back know.

1559
02:12:42,115 --> 02:12:47,995
I don't want to loose
side of the roof tops.

1560
02:12:48,037 --> 02:12:53,167
